<h1>Blacksmithing</h1>

<ol type=1><p>

<li>Show how to build fire in a forge using either charcoal, coal, or wood.<p>

<li>List the operations in forging, and the corresponding tools to be used.<p>

<li>Make a tent hook, stock 3/8" in diameter.<p>

<li>Make a simple hunting knife, or a small bolo.<p>

<li>Make a lap welded ring of 1/4" stock (5" in diameter).<p>

<li>Make a color scale for tempering different tools. For example: tool, color, temperature, bath, uses.<p>

<li>Demonstrate how to temper the following tools according to the temperature scale: knife, bolo, ax, iron bar, hatchet, cold chisel.</ol></span><p>
